@startuml State Diagram – Graph Execution Lifecycle
title TradingAgents — Graph Execution & Memory Lifecycle States

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor AliceBlue
  BorderColor SteelBlue
  ArrowColor SteelBlue
}

[*] --> Idle

state Idle : TradingAgentsGraph constructed\nLLMs initialized\nworkflow compiled

Idle --> ResolvingPending : propagate(ticker, date) called

state ResolvingPending : Check TradingMemoryLog\nfor prior PENDING entries\nfor this ticker

state ResolvingCheck <<choice>>
ResolvingPending --> ResolvingCheck

ResolvingCheck --> Reflecting : pending entries found\n(prices now available)
ResolvingCheck --> InitializingState : no pending entries

state Reflecting : Fetch actual returns (yfinance)\nCompute raw_return + alpha vs SPY\nLLM reflects on each prior decision\nMemory log updated: PENDING→RESOLVED

Reflecting --> InitializingState

state InitializingState : Propagator.create_initial_state()\nInjects past_context from memory log\nCreates AgentState with empty reports\nSets up InvestDebateState + RiskDebateState

InitializingState --> AnalystPhase

state AnalystPhase {
  [*] --> MarketAnalysis
  state MarketAnalysis : LLM tool loop\nget_stock_data + get_indicators\nmarket_report populated

  MarketAnalysis --> SocialAnalysis
  state SocialAnalysis : LLM tool loop\nnews/sentiment sources\nsentiment_report populated

  SocialAnalysis --> NewsAnalysis
  state NewsAnalysis : LLM tool loop\nget_news + get_global_news\nnews_report populated

  NewsAnalysis --> FundamentalsAnalysis
  state FundamentalsAnalysis : LLM tool loop\nget_fundamentals + financials\nfundamentals_report populated

  FundamentalsAnalysis --> [*]
}

AnalystPhase --> DebatePhase

state DebatePhase {
  [*] --> InvestmentDebate
  state InvestmentDebate : Bull ↔ Bear alternation\nN rounds (configurable)\nResearchManager synthesizes → ResearchPlan

  InvestmentDebate --> TraderProposal
  state TraderProposal : Trader generates TraderProposal\nwith entry_price, stop_loss, sizing

  TraderProposal --> RiskDebate
  state RiskDebate : Agg → Con → Neu rotation\nM rounds (configurable)\nPortfolioManager synthesizes → PortfolioDecision

  RiskDebate --> [*]
}

DebatePhase --> Finalizing

state Finalizing : SignalProcessor extracts 5-tier rating\nJSON result logged to disk\nTradingMemoryLog.store_decision() called\n(entry marked PENDING)

Finalizing --> Idle : returns (final_state, signal_dict)

state CheckpointSuspended : Graph suspended at node\nSQLite checkpoint written\n(if checkpoint_enabled=True)

AnalystPhase --> CheckpointSuspended : interrupt_after analyst\n(if configured)
CheckpointSuspended --> AnalystPhase : resume from checkpoint

note right of CheckpointSuspended
  Checkpoint allows inspection
  and resumption mid-graph.
  Enabled via config["checkpoint_enabled"]
end note

@enduml
